<br>
If the damage bonuses don't change, then you should take into account that Albion is neutral to slash for all armor types, and Hibernia scale is vulnerable to slash while Hibernia reinforced is vulnerable to crush. That seems to indicate that slash is the win over all in terms of bonus damage (unless you're a bard killing specialist).<br>
<br>
I went with hammer because I think cleavers look dumb for dwarves (they're OK for trolls though). <p>Gotter Dammerung - 50 skald<br />
