<br>
It’s a tough call.  Both are good.  I have no experience with Sword so I really can’t say, but all the sword-lovers also tend to have Ragnorok, so I guess going 50 in sword is suggested.  But as others have said, wait for the upcoming style review before making any decisions.  <br>
<br>
